.TH HSH 1 "December 2025" "1.0" "Simple Shell Manual"
.SH NAME
hsh \- simple command interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hsh
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hsh
is a simple command line interpreter. It displays a prompt and waits for commands.
.PP
Commands must include the full path (like /bin/ls).
.SH USAGE
Run the shell:
.PP
.RS
./hsh
.RE
.PP
Type commands with full paths. Press Ctrl+D to exit.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
.RS
($) /bin/ls
.br
file1 file2
.br
($) /bin/pwd
.br
/home/user
.RE
.SH AUTHORS
See AUTHORS file
.SH SEE ALSO
sh(1), bash(1), execve(2)
